Content of directories:
- scripts         
     --> all public scripts
- scripts/helpers 
     --> all non-public scripts
- scripts/target/current-state
     --> shared state between scripts, e.g. current StackId
- scripts/target/tmp-output
     --> temporary output from scripts, not intended to be shared


Public scripts ...
- ... must start with 
        cd `dirname ${BASH_SOURCE[0]}`
        . ./shmack_env
- ... may use any number of helper scripts






